==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà nàn bù sĭ, bì yŏu hòu fú

===Proverb===
'''[[大難]][[不]][[死]]，[[必]][[有]][[後]][[福]]'''

# Those who survive a catastrophy are bound to have good fortune later on.

===Alternate forms===
[[大难不死，必有后福]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

